2026-02-20 11:21:39 - INFO - 716 -{"tools": [], "type": "LLMCall", "messages": [{"content": "You are a Travel Planner. Create day-by-day itineraries based on destination and duration.\n\nProvide:\n- Daily schedule (morning/afternoon/evening activities)\n- Hotel options (budget/mid-range/luxury) with prices\n- Budget breakdown: accommodation, food, transport, attractions, total\n- Realistic time estimates\n\nBe concise and practical.", "role": "system"}, {"role": "user", "name": "user", "content": "I want to two day trip to goa with the budget of 50000. Can you help me plan it?"}], "response": {"id": "chatcmpl-e6e01064-92d4-4496-ab37-a3186537f323", "choices": [{"finish_reason": "stop", "index": 0, "logprobs": null, "message": {"content": "Here's a suggested 2-day itinerary for a trip to Goa with a budget of 50,000:\n\n**Day 1:**\n\n* Morning: Arrive at Dabolim Airport, transfer to hotel ( approx. 1 hour)\n* 10:00 AM: Check-in at hotel (suggest: Mid-range - Lemon Tree Hotel, price: 6,000 per night)\n* 11:00 AM: Visit Calangute Beach (free entry)\n* 2:00 PM: Lunch at a local restaurant (approx. 500 per person)\n* 4:00 PM: Visit Fort Aguada (entry fee: 50 per person)\n* 7:00 PM: Dinner at a local restaurant (approx. 500 per person)\n* 9:00 PM: Explore the night market at Baga Beach (free entry)\n\n**Day 2:**\n\n* 9:00 AM: Breakfast at hotel\n* 10:00 AM: Visit Old Goa (free entry)\n* 12:30 PM: Lunch at a local restaurant (approx. 500 per person)\n* 2:30 PM: Water sports at Baga Beach (approx. 1,500 per person)\n* 5:00 PM: Visit Anjuna Beach (free entry)\n* 7:30 PM: Farewell dinner at a local restaurant (approx. 500 per person)\n* 9:30 PM: Departure from Goa\n\n**Hotel Options:**\n\n* Budget: Hotel Palacio De Goa (price: 3,000 per night)\n* Mid-range: Lemon Tree Hotel (price: 6,000 per night)\n* Luxury: The Leela Goa (price: 15,000 per night)\n\n**Budget Breakdown:**\n\n* Accommodation (1 night): 12,000 (mid-range)\n* Food (2 days): 8,000 (approx. 2,000 per meal)\n* Transport (airport transfers, local travel): 4,000\n* Attractions: 1,600 (entry fees, water sports)\n* Total: 25,600\n\nThis leaves you with 24,400 for additional expenses, such as shopping, tips, and any changes to the itinerary.\n\n**Realistic Time Estimates:**\n\n* Travel time from airport to hotel: 1 hour\n* Travel time between attractions: 30 minutes to 1 hour\n* Time spent at each attraction: 1-2 hours\n\nNote: Prices are approximate and may vary depending on the season and availability. This itinerary is customizable to fit your preferences and budget.", "refusal": null, "role": "assistant", "annotations": null, "audio": null, "function_call": null, "tool_calls": null}}], "created": 1771566703, "model": "llama-3.3-70b-versatile", "object": "chat.completion", "service_tier": "on_demand", "system_fingerprint": "fp_68f543a7cc", "usage": {"completion_tokens": 531, "prompt_tokens": 134, "total_tokens": 665, "completion_tokens_details": null, "prompt_tokens_details": null, "queue_time": 0.048235908, "prompt_time": 0.006408412, "completion_time": 1.4559936439999999, "total_time": 1.462402056}, "usage_breakdown": null, "x_groq": {"id": "req_01khwsn74pf8s81b0xg8armxaq", "seed": 261209462}}, "prompt_tokens": 134, "completion_tokens": 531, "agent_id": "Travel_Planner_cc3c8589-404a-4da2-b535-a638fe4db743/cc3c8589-404a-4da2-b535-a638fe4db743"}
